data.description: Great opportunity to live in the popular Charleston Crossing neighborhood! 3 bedroom ranch boasts an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings with a spacious great room and dining room combo. Cheerful kitchen with natural light in breakfast area includes a pantry. Master suite has a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with double sinks. The two additional bedrooms are well sized and one could be an in-home office. The well manicured back yard has a fence, wood deck and space for outdoor fun. New furnance (12/22), new central air (6/23), new water heater (11/22), and new garage door opener (11/23). Close walk to restaurants, shopping, and Nickel Plate District.
